# Welcome to Textella

Textella is an offline PDF reader that converts text to speech directly on your device, ensuring a seamless and private reading experience without the need for an internet connection.

## Key Features
- **Offline Functionality:** No need for an internet connection to use the app.
- **Privacy Focused:** All data stays on your device â€” your privacy is our priority.
- **Text-to-Speech:** Simply pick your PDF file, and Textella will read it out loud to you.

## Need Help?
For any questions or assistance, feel free to contact us at [support@lecfy.com](mailto:support@lecfy.com) with subject "Textella".

Thank you for choosing Textella for your on-device text-to-speech needs!
